TC_1:verify Homepage loads successfully
steps
1.navigate to https://www.zoho.com
2.wait for the page to fully load
3.verify the page title displays zoho
4.verify main navigation menu is visible
5.verify footer is visible and complete
*Expected Result* Homepage loads without errors , all UI elements visible and properly positioned

TC_2: verify navigation menu functionality
1.on homepage , click on "products" menu
2.verify product page loads with list of zoho products
3.click on "resources"
4.verify resources page loads
5.click on "partners"
6.verify partners page loads
*Expected Result* All menu items are clickable and navigate to correct pages

TC_3: Search Functionality on Homepage
1.on homepage,locate search box
2.enter search query "CRM"
3.press enter or click search button
4.verify search results page loads
5.verify results contain CRM-related products/content
6.click on one of the results
7.verify correct page opens
*Expected Result* All products are displayed with complete information and details page opens

TC_4: Sign Up process-New User
1.click on "sign up" button on homepage
2.verify sign up page loads
3.enter valid email address
4.enter valid password
5.enter full name
6.select country from dropdown
7.Accept terms and conditions checkbox
8.click "create account" button
9.verify account creation success message
